quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  76,23,"“Ndithu Ife taivumbulutsa kwa iwe Qur’an mwapang’onopang’ono (kuti uisunge bwino, usaiwale)"
  76,24,"“Choncho, pirira ndi lamulo la Mbuye wako ndipo usamvere wamachimo kapena wokanira aliyense mwa iwo"
  76,25,"“Ndipo kumbukira dzina la Mbuye wako; mmawa, ndi madzulo (Swala za Subuhi, Dhuhr ndi Asri)"
  76,26,"“Ndipo usiku mlambire Iye, (Swala ya Maghrib ndi Isha); ndiponso umulemekeze usiku nthawi yaitali (popemphera sunna za tahajjudi)"
  76,27,"“Ndithu awa akukonda moyo wa dziko lapansi, ndipo akulisiya kumbuyo kwao tsiku lovuta"
  76,28,“Ife ndi amene tidawalenga ndipo tidalimbika kalengedwe kawo; ndipo titafuna tingabweretse ena onga iwo (omvera Allah) kulowa m’malo mwawo
  76,29,“Ndithu ichi ndichikumbutso choncho amene afuna atsata njira yopitira kwa Mbuye wake (pomukhulupirira ndi kumumvera)
  76,30,"“Koma simungafune nokha chilichonse pokhapokha atafuna Allah, ndithu Allah ndi Wodziwa zedi, Wanzeru zakuya"
  76,31,“Akumlowetsa amene wamfuna ku chifundo Chake; koma oyipa wawalinganizira chilango chowawa kwambiri